isle-0-0-100-151.jpg" width="100" height="151" alt="GRAPHIC : PHOTO : GRAD : Brittany Entwisle" title="GRAPHIC : PHOTO : GRAD : Brittany Entwisle" style="float: left; margin: 1px 8px;"><span class="highlight">Brittany Entwisle</span><br> Brittany is graduating from Woodrow Wilson High School. In the fall she will be attending Portland Community College, with the intent to transfer to George Fox University to study Nursing and Children's Ministry.</p><p><br><br></p><p><img src="http://www.pcctoday.com/monkimage.php?mediaDirectory=mediafiles&amp;mediaId=2232669&amp;fileName=graphic--photo--grad--hannah-kenyon-0-0-100-150.jpg" width="100" height="150" alt="GRAPHIC : PHOTO : GRAD : Hannah Kenyon" title="GRAPHIC : PHOTO : GRAD : Hannah Kenyon" style="float: left; margin: 1px 8px;"><span class="highlight">Hannah Kenyon</span><br> Hannah is graduating from Woodrow Wilson High SChool. She will be attending Portland Community College in the fall, with the intent to transfer to Northwest University.</p><p>&nbsp;<br><br></p><p><img src="http://www.pcctoday.com/monkimage.php?mediaDirectory=mediafiles&amp;mediaId=2232681&amp;fileName=graphic--photo--grad--rebecca-landis-0-0-100-150.jpg" width="100" height="150" alt="GRAPHIC : PHOTO : GRAD : Rebecca Landis" title="GRAPHIC : PHOTO : GRAD : Rebecca Landis" style="float: left; margin: 1px 8px;"><span class="highlight">Rebecca Landis</span><br> Rebecca is graduating from Glenco High School. In the fall, she will be attending George Fox University, majoring in Nursing.</p><p>&nbsp;<br><br><br></p><p><img src="http://www.pcctoday.com/monkimage.php?mediaDirectory=mediafiles&amp;mediaId=2232685&amp;fileName=graphic--photo--grad--conner-nielsen-0-0-100-150.jpg" width="100" height="150" alt="GRAPHIC : PHOTO : GRAD : Conner Nielsen" title="GRAPHIC : PHOTO : GRAD : Conner Nielsen" style="float: left; margin: 1px 8px;"><span class="highlight">Conner Nielsen</span><br> Conner is graduating from Milwaukie Academy of the Arts. He will be a