<p><strong>How To Check In Your Child</strong></p>
<p>Preschool and Elementary Kids both check-in at our secure check-in locations. We have three check in locations: upstairs by the main entrance, downstairs by the gym entrance, and downstairs at our Adventure Kids Church room. Children who are three years old or younger check in upstairs in our Professional Nursery. If you need directions, we will have greeters at every entrance that would be happy to direct you to the best check-in location for you.&nbsp;<strong>[ <a href="http://www.pcctoday.com/ministries/children/">more info about check in and security</a> ]&nbsp;</strong></p>
