<li><strong>Every kid gets a prize!</strong> What more could any kid ask for? In addition to the free bible bucks they get this week, kids can earn Bible Bucks each week at our Kids Church and redeem them from "The Store". Kids also have the opportunity to give and provide for a hungry kid somewhere in the world.&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Yummy snacks in between sessions</strong>. Kids are welcome to eat a donut, drink chocolate milk or juice in between the first and second Kids Church sessions. If mom or dad would rather they not have a treat, no problem, just let us know.</li>
